_sText:
The .NAV file is already included in the map - don't generate one yourself!

I never found a fy_iceworld2k for CS:S that resembled 'the most' to the original, so I started to work on what could be considered a 'direct port'. Development actually began back in 2016, but I took a two-year hiatus while working on maps for the classic Counter-Strike game. Now I decided to get back and finish this map, renaming it into "fy_iceworld2k18".
